{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotations:","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1833"},"role":"symbol","title":"removeAnnotations:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"array must conform to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotations:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations in the array."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotations:","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"}}}